Reis, Inc.: Reis, Inc. Launches “Transaction Analytics™” for Commercial Property Sales; Product Empowers Investors and Portfolio Managers to Create Custom Commercial Real Estate Sales Trend and Forecast Analyses








 






1185 Avenue of the Americas
  30th Floor
  New York, NY 10036
  Tel: 212.921.1122
  Fax: 212.921.2533
www.reis.com





